a long nose, beard, two wandering eyebrows, and two eyes with jealous pupils. The description is incomplete in the source text.'),('0- _25_p028_a003fe3c','sculpture','statue','bronze','camel','Late Antiquity','unknown','0-آثارنا المنهوبة_25.pdf',28,''),('0- _25_p029_7a71fcd3','jewelry','ring','bronze','human','Late Antiquity','unknown','0-آثارنا المنهوبة_25.pdf',29,''),('0- _25_p030_6a5dc758','sculpture','statue','bronze','human','Late Antiquity','4th century','0-آثارنا المنهوبة_25.pdf',30,''),('0- _25_p031_d07c367c','object','unknown','unknown','none','unknown','unknown','0-آثارنا المنهوبة_25.pdf',31,''),('0- _25_p032_c737ed55','object','unknown','unknown','none','unknown','unknown','0-آثارنا المنهوبة_25.pdf',32,''),('0- _25_p033_facfb986','sculpture','statue','bronze','none','Late Antiquity','unknown','0-آثارنا المنهوبة_25.pdf',33,''),('0- _25_p034_200fc292','object','unknown','unknown','none','unknown','unknown','0-آثارنا المنهوبة_25.pdf',34,''),('0- _25_p035_2f5db211','object','unknown','silver','none','Late Antiquity','unknown','0-آثارنا المنهوبة_25.pdf',35,''),('0- _25_p036_bea25d9f','object','unknown','marble','none','Late Antiquity','unknown','0-آثارنا المنهوبة_25.pdf',36,'Sculptural fragments, bronze and marble stone: two pieces comprising the front of a bronze right foot and a marble stone hand. Third century BC. Dimensions: 6.5 cm and 6 cm.'),('0- _25_p037_76bcbec5','object','unknown','unknown','none','unknown','unknown','0-آثارنا المنهوبة_25.pdf',37,'Lot, art, dimensions 12.7 × 18.5.'),('0- _25_p038_a303509a','vessel','jar','unknown','none','unknown','unknown','0-آثارنا المنهوبة_25.pdf',38,'Jar, burned clay, with a slightly wide outward-flaring nozzle, puffed body, side handles, and decoration of geometric crawling triangles and by-lines painted in black and red.'),('0- _25_p039_21a0fd74','object','unknown','unknown','none','unknown','unknown','0-آثارنا المنهوبة_25.pdf',39,'Object, material not specified. No descriptive information about the object is provided beyond the text “9 - 16 1.66 LOT - ART - 16 1.66 LOT - ART.”'),('0- _25_p040_1772345a','sculpture','statue','bronze','camel','unknown','unknown','0-آثارنا المنهوبة_25.pdf',40,''),('0- _25_p041_16bc353c','sculpture','statue','marble','human','Late Antiquity','unknown','0-آثارنا المنهوبة_25.pdf',41,'Head of a human statue, marble, depicting a male head with a long neck and a partially preserved face. The eyes are indicated by drilled pupils, the nose is pierced, the eyebrows are arched and joined to the nose, the mouth is pierced, and the ears are preserved on both sides.'),('0- _25_p042_a0c5b0df','object','unknown','unknown','none','unknown','unknown','0-آثارنا المنهوبة_25.pdf',42,''),('0- _25_p043_e92bb9bc','sculpture','statue','bronze','camel','Late Antiquity','unknown','0-آثارنا المنهوبة_25.pdf',43,'Animal statue, bronze, depicting a camel with a hard head, a slight mid-back hump, and a strapped small tail behind the hind legs. Metal. Dimensions: 10.2 cm x 9 cm (4 x 3.55 in); additional measurement given as 3.9 in (9.9 cm). Early millennium BCE.'),('0- _25_p044_1394a6c0','object','unknown','unknown','none','unknown','unknown','0-آثارنا المنهوبة_25.pdf',44,'Lot, material not specified. No further object description is provided in the source text.'),('0- _25_p045_eaae26b1','object','unknown','bronze','lion','unknown','unknown','0-آثارنا المنهوبة_25.pdf',45,'Pavilion, bronze, with a nine-line inscription and a composition featuring the stylized forms of a recumbent animal mediated by a palm tree; two holes are present in the upper corners.'),('0- _25_p046_0ea08f6c','object','unknown','unknown','none','unknown','unknown','0-آثارنا المنهوبة_25.pdf',46,'Object type not specified; material not specified. The source text contains only the fragment “6 . 1.1 19.5 LOT - ART . 1.1 19.5 LOT - ART” and does not provide sufficient information to identify the object, its materials, typology, technique, dimensions, or period.'),('0- _25_p047_a4daec26','object','unknown','unknown','human','unknown','unknown','0-آثارنا المنهوبة_25.pdf',47,'Human doll, material not specified. A human doll, recorded as lot 7:1-2-15.8×9×0, with dimensions 15.8 × 9 × 0.'),('0- _25_p048_04475953','object','unknown','unknown','none','unknown','unknown','0-آثارنا المنهوبة_25.pdf',48,'Object, material not specified, with recorded dimensions of 17.4, 13.9, 11.8, 11.3, 11.3, 7.5, and 8 cm.'),('0- _25_p049_2f28b0e7','currency','coin','unknown','human;owl','Late Antiquity','unknown','0-آثارنا المنهوبة_25.pdf',49,'Coin, metal, old Yemeni coin with an owl bird depicted on one face and what appears to be a human face on the other; dated to about the third century BCE. Weight 4.93 g, diameter 15 mm.'),('0- _25_p050_ee11b378','currency','coin','unknown','human','Late Antiquity','unknown','0-آثارنا المنهوبة_25.pdf',50,'Coin, metal. Old Yemeni coin with human face motifs on both sides, one face bearded and the other also bearded. Dated to the second century and the first century BCE. Weight 1.88 g; diameter 11 mm.'),('0- _25_p051_3acdaa81','currency','coin','unknown','human','Late Antiquity','4th century','0-آثارنا المنهوبة_25.pdf',51,'Coin, metal, an old Yemeni coin with one face bearing a human face in relief, apparently wearing an earring. Dated to around the middle of the 4th century to the 3rd century BCE. Dimensions: 11 mm; weight: 1.98 g.'),('0- _25_p052_3bf323d0','currency','coin','unknown','human','Late Antiquity','4th century','0-آثارنا المنهوبة_25.pdf',52,'Coin, metal. Old Yemeni coin with one face bearing an expression of a human face with clear features, apparently wearing an earring. Dated to around the middle of the 4th century to the 3rd century BCE. Diameter 12 mm.'),('0- _25_p053_809895ce','currency','coin','unknown','human','Late Antiquity','4th century','0-آثارنا المنهوبة_25.pdf',53,'Coin, metal. Old Yemeni coin with one face bearing a human face in relief with clear features, apparently wearing an earring. Dated to around the middle of the 4th century to the 3rd century BCE. Diameter 12 mm.'),('0- _25_p054_975a31dd','currency','coin','unknown','human','Late Antiquity','4th century','0-آثارنا المنهوبة_25.pdf',54,'Coin, metal. Old Yemeni coin with one face bearing an expression of a human face, with a clear glimpse, apparently wearing an earring. Dated to around the middle of the 4th century and the 3rd century BCE. Diameter: 12 mm.'),('0- _25_p055_7d7995f7','object','unknown','bronze','lion','unknown','unknown','0-آثارنا المنهوبة_25.pdf',55,'Bronze plaque, with a prominent inscribed frame and a nine-line inscription in barge-line format, measuring 10.2 × 14.4 cm; the text is recorded as beginning with “1-A-L-A-T-A-T-A-D-Y/Y-A-N-E-N-E-E-R-E-R-E-R-N-E-R-N-E-R-N-E-N-E-N-E-N-A-N-A-T-E-N-E-T-E-N-E-N-E-N-E-N-E-N-E-N-E-N-E-N-N-E-N-N-N-N-N-N-N-N-N-N-N-E-N-N-N-E-N-N-E-N-N-E-N-E-E-N-E-E-E-N-N-E-E-”; dated broadly to the first millennium BCE to the early first millennium CE.'),('0- _25_p056_dc2f7b3e','sculpture','statue','unknown','none','unknown','unknown','0-آثارنا المنهوبة_25.pdf',56,'Animal statue, material not specified. An animal statue.'),('0- _25_p057_4b2bc103','sculpture','head','marble','human','Late Antiquity','unknown','0-آثارنا المنهوبة_25.pdf',57,'Gravestones, marble and stone: a group of gravestones including examples with human heads carved in marble, one bearing an unclear inscription, probably the name of the deceased, together with two additional fragments, one in marble and one in stone.'),('0- _25_p058_9c26a93f','sculpture','head','marble','human','unknown','unknown','0-آثارنا المنهوبة_25.pdf',58,'Human gravestones, marble stone, of different sizes, including a group of gravestones with human heads. Three examples are heavily fragmentary, preserving long, prominent noses, two broken eyes, and a small mouth, with most of their parts lost.'),('0- _25_p059_4de81847','object','unknown','stone','human','Late Antiquity','unknown','0-آثارنا المنهوبة_25.pdf',59,'Gravestone, stone. Human tombstone with a carved face in relief, showing a high nose, long pointed features, blind eyes pierced through the eye area, a light smile, a slightly shorter nose, and two eyebrows.'),('0- _25_p060_d921748e','sculpture','statue','bronze','camel','unknown','unknown','0-آثارنا المنهوبة_25.pdf',60,'Animal statue, bronze, depicting a camel with a high head and two prominent ears, the neck encircled by a collar, a sleeve on the back, and the tail held close to the hind legs; an inscription on the right side appears to be in aristocratic script but is unclear.'),('0- _25_p061_d7091d94','jewelry','ring','bronze','none','Late Antiquity','unknown','0-آثارنا المنهوبة_25.pdf',61,'Animal head, bronze. Head fragment of an animal statue, preserving the right side of the head with a clear view of the face. The eyes are rendered as two prominent rounded forms, with a chin below the mouth. One horn and one ear are broken. Rings around the horn are preserved, characteristic of the horned animal represented.'),('0- _25_p062_6e84de98','object','unknown','unknown','none','unknown','unknown','0-آثارنا المنهوبة_25.pdf',62,'Lot, art, with no further object description or material information provided.'),('0- _25_p063_c1d108c1','object','unknown','limestone','human','Late Antiquity','unknown','0-آثارنا المنهوبة_25.pdf',63,'Figurine, limestone, depicting a seated human figure with broken legs, holding an animal-shaped object in both hands above a hole in the base and inserting a fuse into it; described as a sacrificed piece, probably from the 3rd century BC.'),('0- _25_p064_f6ce2f73','sculpture','statue','marble','human','unknown','unknown','0-آثارنا المنهوبة_25.pdf',64,'Statue, marble stone, human figure of a man standing on a rectangular two-level base, with both hands broken; the base bears a two-line blade line inscription. Dimensions: 380 x 160 mm. The object is dated to about 300 BCE to 100 BCE.'),('0- _25_p065_816507df','sculpture','head','marble','human;lion','unknown','unknown','0-آثارنا المنهوبة_25.pdf',65,'Gravestones, marble stone, in the form of human heads carved from marble in different colors, with long prominent noses, some broad, two prominent eyes, and small prominent mouths; three examples have inscriptions written in the pavilion line.'),('0- _25_p066_7c445bf9','object','unknown','gold','none','Late Antiquity','unknown','0-آثارنا المنهوبة_25.pdf',66,''),('0- _25_p067_31aa95b1','sculpture','statue','marble','human','unknown','unknown','0-آثارنا المنهوبة_25.pdf',67,'Human statue head, white marble, with a long neck encircled by three dark circular lines. The head has clear facial features, including apricot-shaped eyes with drilled holes for the missing pupils, eyebrows marked by horizontal lines, puffed cheeks, a puffed mouth, and prominent ears on both sides.'),('0- _25_p068_2be803ae','object','unknown','unknown','none','unknown','unknown','0-آثارنا المنهوبة_25.pdf',68,'Object type and material cannot be determined from the provided text.'),('0- _25_p069_9ad36b3a','object','unknown','marble','none','Late Antiquity','unknown','0-آثارنا المنهوبة_25.pdf',69,'Table, marble stone, round-shaped, with a flat surface and standing on three cylindrical legs; the outer side is vertically marked with lines and shows traces of squid.'),('0- _25_p070_8aeba613','vessel','bowl','bronze','human;owl','Late Antiquity','2nd century','0-آثارنا المنهوبة_25.pdf',70,'Bowl, bronze. Bronze bowl decorated with painted and/or incised motifs of three human figures, three palm trees, two plant motifs, and a snake. Dated to around the 4th to 2nd century BCE.'),('0- _25_p071_6a058638','object','unknown','bronze','none','Late Antiquity','unknown','0-آثارنا المنهوبة_25.pdf',71,'Saddle, bronze. Sacrificed object composed of an old oil-pouring tub fitted with a fuse holder; the end has a handle terminating at the front half of the oak, marked by the horns at the back, the chin below the mouth, and the feet extending forward.'),('0- _25_p072_9919924b','glyptic','seal','stone','none','Late Antiquity','unknown','0-آثارنا المنهوبة_25.pdf',72,'Seal, black stone, rare cylindrical form, perforated for suspension, with a carved surface bearing symbols resembling an accelerator; dimensions 0.8 cm wide x 0.25 cm high (2 cm x 0.6 cm); dated to about 3400–3100 BCE.'),('0- _25_p073_ccc96b0e','sculpture','statue','bronze','camel','South Arabian antiquity','unknown','0-آثارنا المنهوبة_25.pdf',73,'Animal statue, bronze, depicting a camel with a high head and two upright ears, a collar around the neck, and a sleeve-like element over the back. Dated to around the 1st century BC to the 1st century AD.'),('0- _25_p074_35a83904','object','unknown','marble','none','Late Antiquity','unknown','0-آثارنا المنهوبة_25.pdf',74,''),('0- _25_p075_ed367d40','sculpture','statue','marble','human','unknown','unknown','0-آثارنا المنهوبة_25.pdf',75,'Head of a human statue, marble stone, depicting a male head with clear facial features, closed eyes, a long nose, and a small mouth set in a straight horizontal line; the head has a short neck.'),('0- _25_p076_f2310d70','sculpture','statue','unknown','human','unknown','unknown','0-آثارنا المنهوبة_25.pdf',76,''),('0- _25_p077_5321dc89','object','unknown','marble','none','unknown','unknown','0-آثارنا المنهوبة_25.pdf',77,'Stone vessel, marble, conical-shaped with a high crater and a base of larger diameter than the upper opening, without cover, with two knobs at the middle of the body, and showing white-coloured veining in the same stone.'),('0- _25_p078_96776234','currency','coin','silver','human;owl','Late Antiquity','unknown','0-آثارنا المنهوبة_25.pdf',78,'Coins, silver. Old Yemeni coins, one face with an image of an owl and some with Latin letters, the other face likely showing a human face. Dated to around the fourth and third centuries BCE.'),('0- _25_p079_49144713','object','unknown','unknown','none','unknown','unknown','0-آثارنا المنهوبة_25.pdf',79,'Lot, art, material not specified.'),('0- _25_p080_bee8a24e','sculpture','statue','marble','human','unknown','unknown','0-آثارنا المنهوبة_25.pdf',80,'Sculptural fragments, marble stone: heads of human statues of different shapes and sizes, including one smashed and freckled, with a hint, together with a torso of a statue.'),('0- _25_p081_07788e5d','object','unknown','bronze','none','Islamic medieval','unknown','0-آثارنا المنهوبة_25.pdf',81,'Inscription, bronze, 18 × 13 cm, framed; a bronze engraved inscription with a rusted surface, recorded as al-Silwi 3 and associated with the public confession engravings studied by Ibrahim Al-Silwi 3 (Salawi 3), based on an image shown by the late Khalil Al-Zubairi and published without a photograph in the Daci blog.'),('0- _25_p082_810269e6','currency','coin','gold','none','unknown','unknown','0-آثارنا المنهوبة_25.pdf',82,'Coin, gold. Muslim Yemeni dinar, attributed to the reign of Ali Bin Mohammed Al-Salehi and described as belonging to the “right state”; found in Zebed. The coin bears an inscription in semi-Kufic script.'),('0- _25_p083_06963053','currency','coin','gold','none','Islamic medieval','unknown','0-آثارنا المنهوبة_25.pdf',83,'Coin, gold, Muslim Yemeni denar, dated to the reign of al-Sal, daughter of Ahmed al-Salehi, with a semi-Kufic inscription; reportedly found in Jabalah.'),('0- _25_p084_712079d1','object','unknown','unknown','none','unknown','unknown','0-آثارنا المنهوبة_25.pdf',84,'Lot, art, dimensions 14.2 × 23.8.'),('0- _25_p085_f13f7dbe','object','unknown','bronze','bull','unknown','unknown','0-آثارنا المنهوبة_25.pdf',85,'Hooves, bronze. A group of identical oversized bull hooves in bronze, each larger than normal size and larger than a large cube. Two examples have prominent holes above the cube for installation, and three examples are hollow inside, with holes at the back of the cubes and on the foot base.'),('0- _25_p086_d1991843','sculpture','statue','marble','human','Late Antiquity','unknown','0-آثارنا المنهوبة_25.pdf',86,'Human statues, marble stone, lot of human statues carved in marble, similar in design, pose, and size, with one larger central statue distinguished by a pigeon held in the hand; the base bears a single-line inscription reading [A/T/R/R]. Dimensions: 10 × 5.5 × 3 × 7.25 × 3.25 × 1.5.'),('0- _25_p087_a80eaa61','sculpture','statue','marble','horse;human','unknown','unknown','0-آثارنا المنهوبة_25.pdf',87,'Human statues, marble stone, a group of carved marble figures comprising two seated statues, one standing figure beneath them, a bust, a small horse, and a mural with an ox’s head; dimensions recorded as 7 × 4 × 2.5 and 2.5 × 3 × 0.5.'),('0- _25_p088_83fc102a','sculpture','statue','marble','human','Late Antiquity','unknown','0-آثارنا المنهوبة_25.pdf',88,'Two human statues and a face, marble stone, comprising two human statues in a sitting position and an empty-eyed human mask with mouth and nose, all in marble stone.'),('0- _25_p089_96db7973','sculpture','statue','bronze','human;lion','Late Antiquity','unknown','0-آثارنا المنهوبة_25.pdf',89,''),('0- _25_p090_98c5db64','sculpture','statue','bronze','camel','Late Antiquity','unknown','0-آثارنا المنهوبة_25.pdf',90,''),('0- _25_p091_798e2234','object','unknown','marble','human','Late Antiquity','unknown','0-آثارنا المنهوبة_25.pdf',91,''),('0- _25_p092_aac8e3f9','object','unknown','unknown','none','unknown','unknown','0-آثارنا المنهوبة_25.pdf',92,''),('0- _25_p093_28b41208','sculpture','statue','marble','human','Late Antiquity','unknown','0-آثارنا المنهوبة_25.pdf',93,'Human bust, marble stone, depicting a woman with the hands extended forward, hair falling behind the ears, eyes with two recessed pupils, a long nose, and bars; the bust is placed on a separate inscribed base with a three-line inscription.'),('0- _25_p094_3329b4f9','stone monument','tombstone','marble','human','Late Antiquity','unknown','0-آثارنا المنهوبة_25.pdf',94,'Tombstone, marble, with a human face carved in relief or incised on the stone, showing a long nose, eyebrows connected to the beard, two pierced and closed eyes, and a very small mouth.'),('0- _25_p095_9ee6e6c7','stone monument','tombstone','marble','human','unknown','unknown','0-آثارنا المنهوبة_25.pdf',95,'Tombstone, marble stone, with a human face in relief or incised depiction showing a broad long rectangular nose, two visible eyes with indicated pupils, a small mouth, and a wide chin; below the face is a two-line inscription. The object is described as a marble tombstone and is dated to about 200 BCE.'),('0- _25_p096_ca1b4fa3','sculpture','statue','unknown','human','unknown','unknown','0-آثارنا المنهوبة_25.pdf',96,'Head, material not specified. The head of a human statue.'),('0- _25_p097_d944cef5','sculpture','statue','marble','human','Late Antiquity','unknown','0-آثارنا المنهوبة_25.pdf',97,'Human statue face, marble stone, carved in marble, with clear features; the eyes are blind, long and well connected, the eyebrows are strongly joined, the nostrils are open, the mouth is small, and the chin is broad. Dated to about 200 BC–100 BC.'),('0- _25_p098_049174ca','sculpture','statue','marble','human','Late Antiquity','unknown','0-آثارنا المنهوبة_25.pdf',98,'Head of a human statue, marble stone, depicting a male head with a clear face, almond-shaped eyes, packed eyebrows, a long broken nose, closed lips, ears on both sides, and a short neck.'),('0- _26_p001_4890a194','object','unknown','unknown','none','unknown','unknown','0-آثارنا المنهوبة_26.pdf',1,''),('0- _26_p001_c637dc98','object','unknown','unknown','none','unknown','unknown','0-آثارنا المنهوبة_26.pdf',1,''),('0- _26_p001_e0dc0d07','object','unknown','unknown','none','Late Antiquity','unknown','0-آثارنا المنهوبة_26.pdf',1,''),('0- _26_p001_ec47e8a1','object','unknown','unknown','none','Late Antiquity','unknown','0-آثارنا المنهوبة_26.pdf',1,''),('0- _26_p002_9e2d521e','object','unknown','unknown','none','Late Antiquity','unknown','0-آثارنا المنهوبة_26.pdf',2,''),('0- _26_p002_b2a8870f','object','unknown','unknown','none','unknown','unknown','0-آثارنا المنهوبة_26.pdf',2,'