-آثارنا المنهوبة_28.pdf',6,'Object, material not specified, with dimensions 500 x 30 x 45.5 x 8.6–9.7 x 25.1–, inventory number SEM 692, dated 1900 (1898–1899).'),('0- _28_p007_7f5ed1e5','object','unknown','stone','none','unknown','unknown','0-آثارنا المنهوبة_28.pdf',7,'Inscribed stone, stone, rectangular, with 27 lines of inscription; engraved with a clear line and an engraving damaged at the edges.'),('0- _28_p008_fefb8c59','sculpture','head','limestone','bull','unknown','unknown','0-آثارنا المنهوبة_28.pdf',8,'Altar, limestone. Rectangular altar with a bull’s head carved on the front; a long central incision extends from the body of the altar up to the head of the bull, described as a maze.'),('0- _28_p009_d94e3f6b','stone monument','tombstone','limestone','none','Late Antiquity','unknown','0-آثارنا المنهوبة_28.pdf',9,''),('0- _28_p010_29618710','sculpture','head','marble','bull','unknown','unknown','0-آثارنا المنهوبة_28.pdf',10,'Marble wall fragment with relief decoration, carved in marble stone, preserving a sculptural composition of visible motifs including written forms, vegetal ornament, animal figures, five bull heads with short horns arranged on both sides, and bird imagery. The decoration is divided by a blade-like line and includes a central inscription-like element, surrounded by vegetal ornament with grape clusters, birds feeding on grapes, plant forms, and a clearly rendered bull head with small birds also shown eating grapes.'),('0- _28_p011_41cdbb52','object','unknown','marble','none','Late Antiquity','1st century','0-آثارنا المنهوبة_28.pdf',11,''),('0- _28_p012_b3929ea9','object','unknown','stone','none','unknown','unknown','0-آثارنا المنهوبة_28.pdf',12,'Inscription, stone: rectangular stone inscription with three lines of carved text.'),('0- _28_p013_e319240e','object','unknown','marble','none','Late Antiquity','6th century','0-آثارنا المنهوبة_28.pdf',13,''),('0- _28_p014_9cb4bd60','object','unknown','stone','none','Late Antiquity','6th century','0