wn','unknown','0-آثارنا المنهوبة_28.pdf',28,'Statue, bronze. Small statue of a horse in motion with a child rider, the child shown in a pose consistent with the horse’s movement and raising both hands upward and to the side. The horse is missing the limbs of both forelegs and hind legs. Recorded dimensions: 8.4 x 6.2 x 8.5 cm; fish 4.2 cm.'),('0- _28_p029_e567a978','stone monument','tombstone','marble','human','Late Antiquity','unknown','0-آثارنا المنهوبة_28.pdf',29,'Tombstone, marble. Grave marker in the shape of a human face, with engraved oval eyes, measured eyebrows, a sharply defined nose with clear lines, and an applied mouth.'),('0- _28_p030_c03ab137','sculpture','statue','marble','none','South Arabian antiquity','3rd century','0-آثارنا المنهوبة_28.pdf',30,''),('0- _28_p031_19978641','stone monument','tombstone','marble','human','Late Antiquity','unknown','0-آثارنا المنهوبة_28.pdf',31,'Tombstone, marble, carved with a human face in relief, showing a clear facial outline, prominent pupils, a visible nose, open lips, and ears indicated on both sides of the head by parallel curved lines. Dated to the 3rd–1st century BC, with a further attribution to the 1st century.'),('0- _3_p001_42fde02a','sculpture','head','bronze','bull','unknown','unknown','0-آثارنا المنهوبة_3.pdf',1,''),('0- _3_p001_618d8aa0','object','unknown','bronze','human','unknown','unknown','0-آثارنا المنهوبة_3.pdf',1,''),('0- _3_p001_a0a4574c','jewelry','ring','bronze','none','Late Antiquity','unknown','0-آثارنا المنهوبة_3.pdf',1,''),('0- _3_p002_1a5f1c12','sculpture','head','gold','none','Late Antiquity','unknown','0-آثارنا المنهوبة_3.pdf',2,''),('0- _3_p002_915f506a','object','unknown','gold','human','Islamic medieval','unknown','0-آثارنا المنهوبة_3.pdf',2,''),('0- _3_p002_d12a04b2','object','unknown','gold','none','Late Antiquity','unknown','0-آثارنا المنهوبة_3.pdf',2,''),('0- _3_p003_38bfbdc5','object','unknown','gold','none','Late Antiquity','unknown','0-آثارنا المنهوبة_3.pdf',3,''),('0- _3_p0