iquity','unknown','0-آثارنا المنهوبة_4.pdf',2,''),('0- _4_p003_16facb8e','sculpture','statue','marble','lion','Late Antiquity','unknown','0-آثارنا المنهوبة_4.pdf',3,'Statue, marble stone. Woman’s statue depicting a seated female figure on a chair of the same material. The figure is described as clear-cut, with a low-cut garment, thinning form, and cuffed sleeves; the surface is noted as hairy. The object is associated with Barkat House and is recorded as missing. Photo number 6.'),('0- _4_p003_54637cdc','sculpture','statue','bronze','none','unknown','unknown','0-آثارنا المنهوبة_4.pdf',3,''),('0- _4_p004_16ec014b','sculpture','statue','stone','none','Late Antiquity','unknown','0-آثارنا المنهوبة_4.pdf',4,''),('0- _4_p004_44b0f2d6','sculpture','statue','marble','none','unknown','unknown','0-آثارنا المنهوبة_4.pdf',4,''),('0- _4_p005_65368b4e','sculpture','statue','limestone','none','unknown','unknown','0-آثارنا المنهوبة_4.pdf',5,''),('0- _4_p005_84a0ac5e','stone monument','tombstone','marble','none','Late Antiquity','unknown','0-آثارنا المنهوبة_4.pdf',5,''),('0- _4_p006_c70aabec','sculpture','statue','marble','none','unknown','unknown','0-آثارنا المنهوبة_4.pdf',6,''),('0- _4_p006_e4581251','object','unknown','unknown','none','unknown','unknown','0-آثارنا المنهوبة_4.pdf',6,''),('0- _4_p007_132cc91e','object','unknown','unknown','none','unknown','unknown','0-آثارنا المنهوبة_4.pdf',7,''),('0- _4_p007_94931a8a','stone monument','tombstone','stone','none','Late Antiquity','unknown','0-آثارنا المنهوبة_4.pdf',7,''),('0- _4_p008_9905cdb4','stone monument','tombstone','limestone','none','Late Antiquity','unknown','0-آثارنا المنهوبة_4.pdf',8,'Tombstone, limestone. Tombstone for a man, carved in limestone, with a face rendered in relief and inscribed with letters arranged in a line across the face. The description mentions a clear face, two eyes, two oval lips, and a high-profile album, with the inscription identified as “Jerry’s Stone.”'),('0- _4_p008_edea912b','sculpture','statue','stone','none','unknown','unknown','0-آثارنا المنهوبة_4.pdf',8,'Statue, granite stone, described as a statue in granite stone with a pale white surface and red state; the source text also mentions cheek, eyes, and a global auction in Britain, but the description is otherwise unclear and fragmentary.'),('0- _4_p009_6c2e0f24','sculpture','statue','bronze','human','unknown','unknown','0-آثارنا المنهوبة_4.pdf',9,''),('0- _4_p009_90e33534','sculpture','head','marble','none','unknown','unknown','0-آثارنا المنهوبة_4.pdf',9,'Sculptural fragment, marble, in the shape of Thor’s head, with a clear-cut form and broken horns. The object is described as part of a polished marble stone.'),('0- _4_p010_469326ea','object','unknown','stone','none','unknown','unknown','0-آثارنا المنهوبة_4.pdf',10,''),('0- _4_p010_a7693691','stone monument','tombstone','stone','human','Late Antiquity','unknown','0-آثارنا المنهوبة_4.pdf',10,''),('0- _4_p011_1d3c0b89','object','unknown','stone','none','unknown','unknown','0-آثارنا المنهوبة_4.pdf',11,''),('0- _4_p011_cca5589b','sculpture','statue','limestone','human;owl','Late Antiquity','unknown','0-آثارنا المنهوبة_4.pdf',11,''),('0- _5_p001_6d116178','sculpture','statue','bronze','none','Late Antiquity','unknown','0-آثارنا المنهوبة_5.pdf',1,'Statue, bronze, of a standing man in motion, with a clear face, muzzle, hair, wrinkle, and sailor attributes as described in the source text. The object is recorded as missing. It is dated to the second century BCE and attributed to the southern Arabian Peninsula (old Yemen). Dimensions: 13.5 cm long.'),('0- _5_p001_9cc546a5','stone monument','tombstone','marble','none','Late Antiquity','unknown','0-آثارنا المنهوبة_5.pdf',1,'Tombstone, marble, fragmentary, with incised inscription and relief decoration; described as a man’s tombstone, preserving part of the deceased’s name with the letter “N” visible in the final line, and featuring a human face motif with prominent eyes, a small mouth, and a strand or line beneath the mouth. Provenance is given as the southern Arabian Peninsula (old Yemen). Length 27.5 cm.'),('0- _5_p002_883e543c','stone monument','tombstone','marble','none','unknown','unknown','0-آثارنا المنهوبة_5.pdf',2,'Statue head, marble: head of a male statue with a long neck, carved in marble; the face has high eyebrows, prominent eyes, a prominent nose, and a small mouth, with hair rendered in a clear, salty tombstone-like treatment.'),('0- _5_p002_ff306543','sculpture','statue','stone','human','Late Antiquity','unknown','0-آثارنا المنهوبة_5.pdf',2,''),('0- _5_p003_0a6629b7','sculpture','statue','bronze','none','Late Antiquity','unknown','0-آثارنا المنهوبة_5.pdf',3,'Statue, bronze, depicting two adjoining lizards connected at the tail and shown in motion. The object is almost 10 cm in diameter.'),('0- _5_p003_5f667732','stone monument','tombstone','marble','none','Late Antiquity','unknown','0-آثارنا المنهوبة_5.pdf',3,'Grave marker head, polished marble, in the form of a man’s head with a short neck, defined head, indicated hair, eyebrows, a prominent nose, and closed mouth, decorated with two lizards and two rosettes; from the Horn of the Arabian Peninsula (old Yemen); length 22 cm.'),('0- _5_p004_a120f029','object','unknown','stone','none','Islamic medieval','2nd century','0-آثارنا المنهوبة_5.pdf',4,'Palette, stone, with incised and carved decoration, 28 cm high and 23 cm wide, from the southern Arabian Peninsula (old Yemen), dated to the 2nd century AD. The object is described as a palette with drawings, showing sculptural decoration and a three-line inscription on the anthem line reading NFS, NBYR, BAT, BA, B.'),('0- _5_p004_b5ff189c','sculpture','statue','stone','none','Late Antiquity','unknown','0-آثارنا المنهوبة_5.pdf',4,'Statue head, stone, of a male figure with a clearly modeled face and distinct eyes; carved in stone, from the southern Arabian Peninsula (ancient Yemen), dated to the 3rd century B.C.E., and measuring almost 20 cm in height.'),('0- _5_p005_882c4e9e','inscribed object','plaque','marble','none','unknown','unknown','0-آثارنا المنهوبة_5.pdf',5,'Plaque, marble. Rectangular polished marble plaque with a base of the same stone, bearing five letters: “A click and HBL” and the inscription “Horn A and Miledi - Southern Arabian Peninsula (old Yemen).” Height 36 cm.'),('0- _5_p005_a2429582','sculpture','statue','marble','none','Late Antiquity','unknown','0-آثارنا المنهوبة_5.pdf',5,''),('0- _5_p006_818e1ef4','stone monument','tombstone','marble','none','Late Antiquity','unknown','0-آثارنا المنهوبة_5.pdf',6,'Tombstone, marble, cylindrical in shape, with a clear-cut surface, two perforations, and a small incised mouth; described as having a distinctive character in the making of gravestones. Origin: southern Arabian Peninsula (old Yemen). Height 18 cm. Missing.'),('0- _5_p006_95a38b81','sculpture','statue','stone','none','Late Antiquity','5th century','0-آثارنا المنهوبة_5.pdf',6,'Animal statue, stone. Statue of an animal on a rectangular base of the same material, with large horns visible; described as a “glimpse of big horns wrapped up.” Stone, 32.5 cm high. Dated to the 5th century B.C.E. and attributed to the southern Arabian Peninsula (old Yemen).'),('0- _5_p007_712e95bc','stone monument','tombstone','stone','none','Late Antiquity','unknown','0-آثارنا المنهوبة_5.pdf',7,'Tombstone, stone. Rectangular tombstone carved in low relief with a clear-cut discharge, featuring eyes, a prominent nose, and a semi-open mouth; inscribed with three letters reading p.P.R. Late 2000 BCE. Length 45.5 cm.'),('0- _5_p007_764a5e88','object','unknown','bronze','none','Late Antiquity','4th century','0-آثارنا المنهوبة_5.pdf',7,'Object, bronze. Curved handle ending in an animal body with large horns curved backwards; two hands placed in front of a lumbar area bearing a three-letter inscription. Sacrificed. Dated to the 4th century B.C.E.'),('0- _5_p008_3ad06fef','stone monument','tombstone','marble','none','Late Antiquity','unknown','0-آثارنا المنهوبة_5.pdf',8,'Tombstone, marble. Rectangular tombstone carved from a marble stone, from the Horn of the Arabian Peninsula (old Yemen). Length 38.2 cm.'),('0- _5_p008_678e2b28','sculpture','statue','bronze','none','Late Antiquity','2nd century','0-آثارنا المنهوبة_5.pdf',8,''),('0- _5_p009_16162ad0','jewelry','ring','unknown','none','Late Antiquity','unknown','0-آثارنا المنهوبة_5.pdf',9,'Metal artifact, metal, rectangular conglomerate on four legs, with edges decorated with geometric shapes; the sides are covered with a walrus-enveloped decorator and a restaurant with prominent animal head feces, and the inter-lettered emptiness includes various plant decorative elements.'),('0- _5_p009_e7a20612','sculpture','head','silver','none','unknown','unknown','0-آثارنا المنهوبة_5.pdf',9,'Sword, polished metal and silver, with a blade of polished metal and a silver hilt or head decorated with silver filaments.'),('0- _7_p001_5960eb81','sculpture','statue','bronze','none','Late Antiquity','1st century','0-آثارنا المنهوبة_7.pdf',1,''),('0- _7_p002_6cd79c3e','sculpture','bust','bronze','none','Late Antiquity','unknown','0-آثارنا المنهوبة_7.pdf',2,''),('0- _7_p003_ba0a0c53','sculpture','statue','unknown','none','South Arabian antiquity','unknown','0-آثارنا المنهوبة_7.pdf',3,''),('0- _7_p004_d9ae2b59','stone monument','tombstone','stone','none','unknown','unknown','0-آثارنا المنهوبة_7.pdf',4,''),('0- _7_p005_52354a90','stone monument','tombstone','stone','none','Late Antiquity','unknown','0-آثارنا المنهوبة_7.pdf',5,''),('0- _7_p006_bf9a00d0','stone monument','tombstone','stone','none','South Arabian antiquity','unknown','0-آثارنا المنهوبة_7.pdf',6,''),('0- _8_p001_c66e5369','glyptic','seal','marble','none','unknown','unknown','0-آثارنا المنهوبة_8.pdf',1,''),('0- _8_p001_f26b683a','object','unknown','marble','none','unknown','unknown','0-آثارنا المنهوبة_8.pdf',1,''),('0- _8_p002_21b4a2f4','sculpture','bust','marble','horse','Islamic medieval','unknown','0-آثارنا المنهوبة_8